## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="188b0-102">다음 표에서 현재 지원 되는 옵션을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-102">The following table shows the currently supported options.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="188b0-103">범주</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-103">Category</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="188b0-104">설정</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-104">Setting</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="188b0-105">값/효과</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-105">Value/effect</span></span>|  
|--------------|-------------|-------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="188b0-106">계약(contract)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-106">contract</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="188b0-107">상속</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-107">inheritance</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="188b0-108">`true` 입력 시 계약 상속을 설정 하려면 `false` 전원을 끕니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-108">`true` to turn contract inheritance on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="188b0-109">기본값은 `true`입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-109">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="188b0-110">런타임(runtime)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-110">runtime</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="188b0-111">확인</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-111">checking</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="188b0-112">`true` 입력 시 런타임 검사를 설정 하려면 `false` 전원을 끕니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-112">`true` to turn run-time checking on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="188b0-113">기본값은 `true`입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-113">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="188b0-114">다음 예제와 같이이 특성을 사용할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-114">You can use this attribute as illustrated in the following examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="188b0-115">런타임 전체 어셈블리에 대 한 검사를 끄려면:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-115">To turn off run-time checking for the entire assembly:</span></span>  
  
```  
[assembly:ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="188b0-116">켜려면 런타임 계약 확인을 특정 형식에 대 한</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-116">To turn run-time contract checking on for a specific type:</span></span>  
  
```  
   [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", true)]  
   class TypeWithRuntimeChecking {  
  
       ...  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="188b0-117">런타임 검사 사용 하지 않으려면 특정 메서드에 대:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="188b0-117">To turn run-time checking off for a specific method:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Turn off all contract inheritance from interface IList<T>  
[ContractOption("contract", "inheritance", false)]  
class MyConcurrentList<T> : IList<T> {  
   ...  
}  
  
[ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
public override MyMethod(int x) {  
   // no inherited contracts checked at runtime,  
   // no invariants checked at runtime.  
   ...  
}  
  
       [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
       public void MethodWithoutRuntimeChecking(...) {  
          ...  
       }  
   }  
  
```
